{"tid":939562,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中方證實對加拿大公民康明凱及邁克爾採取強制措施","createTime":"2018-12-13T08:41:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-13T08:52:57.000Z","uid":39464,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9b68ae6b443409638d61f9ffd6728532bb4f1219","tid":939562,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T08:41:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1433142_1_20181213154919.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1433142_1_20181213154919.jpg&h=f93c9627&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部發言人陸慷證實，兩名加拿大公民被中國拘留。<br />\n<br />\n陸慷說，國際危機組織東北亞高級顧問、加拿大前外交人員康明凱，以及加拿大商人邁克爾，涉嫌從事危害中國國家安全的活動，依據中國《刑法》 及《 刑事訴訟法》規定，分別被北京市及遼寧省丹東市國家安全局，採取強制措施，兩宗案件正在偵辦之中，兩地的國安部門亦已通知加拿大駐華使館，兩人的合法權益得到保障。<br />\n<br />\n被問到兩人被捕，是否與華為副董事長孟晚舟在加拿大被扣押有關，陸慷說，中國是依法依規採取行動。<br />\n<br />\n至於康明凱與邁克爾兩人都曾從事與北韓有關的工作，兩人被捕的案件是否有關，陸慷並無正面回應。<br />\n<br />\n對於有在內地的加拿大人表示擔心安全，陸康回應說，中方一貫對外交往持積極態度，外國人只要遵守中國的法律法規，沒有甚麼好擔心。他說，今年至11月加拿大來華共有78萬人次，中國是否安全，加拿大人心中有數，反而是孟晚舟事件後，很多中國人懷疑加拿大是否安全。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1433142-20181213.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1433142-20181213.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=jWio4OM9S%2BpzTTpU6lxKIDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=08ea11d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1433142-20181213.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=1bc8c9f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1433142-20181213.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"e41a7d5511b8ad3852a77a36cf883e26dbcf0a3d","tid":939562,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T08:42:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">This is WAR！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span></span></span>"},{"pid":"dbaeae833ebb97d850647599f93d720a65c25152","tid":939562,"uid":94828,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T08:43:43.000Z","msg":"反而是孟晚舟事件後，很多中國人懷疑加拿大是否安全。<br />\n<br />\n歡迎死返祖國"},{"pid":"3974f0a88145d68e08fa60c860983c4aabde2d89","tid":939562,"uid":28195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T08:47:09.000Z","msg":"同ISIS 手法一樣"},{"pid":"5ef766937df3d8b46e6eb4ba06a12f62d63e1cf4","tid":939562,"uid":162409,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"dbaeae833ebb97d850647599f93d720a65c25152","tid":939562,"uid":94828,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T08:43:43.000Z","msg":"反而是孟晚舟事件後，很多中國人懷疑加拿大是否安全。<br />\n<br />\n歡迎死返祖國"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T08:47:35.000Z","msg":"支持強制撤僑   全部死返支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ddd8cd672b29bfb6159847fe5449e80e0f038d6","tid":939562,"uid":190629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T08:49:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"29137885db8bb1e7adfb673ff820c8885d3951a5","tid":939562,"uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dbaeae833ebb97d850647599f93d720a65c25152","tid":939562,"uid":94828,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T08:43:43.000Z","msg":"反而是孟晚舟事件後，很多中國人懷疑加拿大是否安全。<br />\n<br />\n歡迎死返祖國"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T08:49:55.000Z","msg":"走還走，資金點都要留加拿大"},{"pid":"4cf40e25e7aac23e53793573551335acd0630695","tid":939562,"uid":34119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T08:51:00.000Z","msg":"聊交打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c09c8baaa6c729f652e7c12246f6d0493bfa2de","tid":939562,"uid":61280,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"cite